			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Pets don't benefit from focus effects on items. The only effects they benefit from are procs. The pet does benefit from AC, hp and resists, but in all likelyhood, the resists will be useless, because the pet will use its owners resists anyway (most of the time).
<br />

